    <item>
      <title>独家：如果利率下降，俄罗斯的VTB将获得数十亿卢布，CFO表示</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russias-vtb-gain-billions-roubles-if-interest-rates-come-down-cfo-says-2025-07-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[CFO DMITRY PYANOV告诉路透社，中央银行的利率每1％削减净利率都会使俄罗斯的VTB银行额外获得200亿卢布（2.5亿美元）的净利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russias-vtb-gain-billions-roubles-if-interest-rates-come-down-cfo-says-2025-07-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Jul 2025 13:19:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利的Credem Bank首席Angelo Campani死于62岁</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italys-credem-bank-chief-angelo-campani-dies-suddenly-aged-62-2025-07-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该银行说，意大利地区银行信贷负责人安吉洛·坎帕尼（Angelo Campani）于周五去世，享年62岁，并补充说，它召集了7月9日的董事会会议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italys-credem-bank-chief-angelo-campani-dies-suddenly-aged-62-2025-07-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Jul 2025 13:17:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
