      <title>意大利贷方bper提升流行音乐会达到63.9亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italian-lender-bper-increases-bid-pop-sondrio-639-billion-2025-07-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该银行周四表示，意大利贷方BPER已将对较小的竞争对手Popolare Di Sondrio的出价提高到54.4亿欧元（63.9亿美元），该银行周四表示，加热了该国金融部门的种族，这已经看到了一系列交易和报价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italian-lender-bper-increases-bid-pop-sondrio-639-billion-2025-07-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Jul 2025 19:59:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蒙特·迪帕斯（Monte dei Paschi）说，拥有35％的Mediobanca就足够了</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/monte-dei-paschi-says-35-ownership-mediobanca-would-be-enough-2025-07-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利国家支持的银行蒙特·德·帕斯基·迪·西耶纳（Monte dei Paschi di Siena）表示，在其买断下，至少要确保Mediobanca资本的至少35％足以控制其目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/monte-dei-paschi-says-35-ownership-mediobanca-would-be-enough-2025-07-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Jul 2025 19:46:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯央行认为没有危险的银行危机的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russian-central-bank-sees-no-risk-looming-banking-crisis-2025-07-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州长Elvira Nabiullina周四表示，俄罗斯中央银行认为，由于银行的1000亿美元资本的不断增长，该国银行体系中危机的危机没有危险的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russian-central-bank-sees-no-risk-looming-banking-crisis-2025-07-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Jul 2025 15:07:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>J.P. Morgan的Morgan持警告Stablecoin的万亿美元增长押注，将其削减了一半</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-wary-stablecoins-trillion-dollar-growth-bets-cuts-them-by-half-2025-07-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[J.P. Morgan周四预测，到2028年，Stablecoin的增长将仅达到5000亿美元，称数万亿美元的预测“太乐观了”，因为几乎没有证据表明主流采用了美元的加密货币标志。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-wary-stablecoins-trillion-dollar-growth-bets-cuts-them-by-half-2025-07-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Jul 2025 13:44:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
