      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Jul 2025 13:36:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>French Fintech Qonto寻求银行许可证，因为它针对2030年的200万客户</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/french-fintech-qonto-seeks-banking-license-it-targets-2-million-clients-by-2030-2025-07-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[它周四表示，法国金融科技Qonto已在法国的银行监管机构申请了银行许可证，因为它试图扩大付款服务以提供贷款，储蓄和投资产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/french-fintech-qonto-seeks-banking-license-it-targets-2-million-clients-by-2030-2025-07-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Jul 2025 12:55:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Amundi警告我们Stablecoin政策可能会破坏全球支付系统的稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/amundi-warns-us-stablecoin-policy-could-destabilise-global-payments-system-2025-07-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲最大的资产经理引起了人们的担忧，即在《美国天才法案》之后，以美元支持的stablecoins繁荣起来可能会导致货币流动的重大转变，从而破坏全球支付系统的稳定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/amundi-warns-us-stablecoin-policy-could-destabilise-global-payments-system-2025-07-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Jul 2025 12:04:50 GMT</pubDate>
